r1 \cdot r2 = <x1, y1> \cdot <x2, y2> = x1*x2 + y1 * y2
r1 \cdot r2 = <||r1||cos(\theta1), ||r1||sin(\theta1)> \cdot <||r2||cos(\theta2), ||r2||sin(\theta2)>
r1 \cdot r2 = ||r1||*||r2|| * cos(\theta1) * cos(\theta2) +  ||r1||*||r2|| * sin(\theta1) * sin(\theta2) 
r1 \cdot r2 = ||r1||*||r2|| * [cos(\theta1) * cos(\theta2) + sin(\theta1) * sin(\theta2)] 
cos(\alpha - \beta) = cos(\alpha) * cos(\beta) + sin(\alpha) * sin(\beta)
